<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <%- include('partials/head') %>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background-color: #f9f6f3;
        }

        .content-wrapper {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }

        .about-container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .about-container h1 {
            font-size: 40px;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .about-container p {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: justify;
        }

        .about-container strong {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
        }

        .tableau-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 50px auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .tableau-container h2 {
            font-size: 28px;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .tableau-container iframe {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 900px;
            height: 600px;
            border: none;
            margin: 20px auto;
        }

        .cta-section {
            margin-top: 50px;
            background-color: #ebe6e2;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .cta-section h3 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .cta-section p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .cta-section a {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #a63636;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 5px;
        }

        .cta-section a:hover {
            background-color: #8c2e2e;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            margin-top: auto;
        }

        footer a {
            color: #a63636;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <!-- Navbar -->
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

    <!-- Content Wrapper -->
    <div class="content-wrapper">
        <div class="about-container">
            <h1>About <strong>Turtle Shelter Project</strong></h1>
            <p>
                The <strong>Turtle Shelter Project</strong> was born from the realization that extreme weather can be life-threatening for individuals
                experiencing homelessness. Each year, countless lives are lost to the cold due to a lack of shelter and proper insulation.
                Our mission is to provide portable, effective, and durable solutions through the distribution of <strong>Turtle Shelter</strong> vests.
            </p>
            <p>
                Inspired by the turtle's ability to carry its shelter wherever it goes, the <strong>Turtle Shelter</strong> vest is a life-saving innovation designed
                to trap body heat, shield from wind, and provide comfort. With the help of dedicated volunteers, generous donors, and supportive
                communities, we've distributed thousands of these vests to individuals in need across Utah and beyond.
            </p>
            <p>
                Together, we can make a meaningful impact by ensuring that no one has to face the cold alone. Join us in this life-saving mission
                to provide hope, warmth, and dignity to those who need it most.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Tableau Dashboard -->
        <div class="tableau-container">
            <h2>Homelessness Statistics</h2>
            <p>
                Understanding the scale of homelessness is the first step to addressing it. Explore our dashboard to see statistics on homelessness
                nationwide and in Utah.
            </p>
            <iframe src="https://public.tableau.com/views/YourDashboardNameHere" title="Homelessness Statistics Dashboard"></iframe>
        </div>

        <!-- Call-to-Action Section -->
        <section class="cta-section">
            <h3>Get Involved with <strong>Turtle Shelter Project</strong></h3>
            <p>
                Whether it’s volunteering your time, donating funds, or spreading the word, every action you take helps save lives.
            </p>
            <a href="/volunteer">Volunteer</a>
            <a href="/donate">Donate</a>
        </section>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
        <p>
            © 2024 Turtle Shelter Project. All rights reserved. 
            <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a> | 
            <a href="/terms">Terms of Service</a>
        </p>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>
